				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">In Natimbi, I have fired arrows at a MoB behind a rock. The arrows will "wait" on my side of the rock, until the MoB is in their path. Then they will hit consectutively. I've had up to 5 arrows do this at once, instantly dropping a MoB a good % of its health. It is not lag, it is probably a graphics glitch, but the arrows aren't poofing or missing... it is a very odd thing.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=669557" target="_blank" class="postlink"><span style="color: blue">Click here</a></span>to see my stuff
