			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">No lol.  I'm dead serrious.  I could go out to CS and show you all.  Should probably go out there and get a screenshot for you.  The arrows will actually sway back and forth hovering against the wall trying to find the mob.  Like I said, none of my arrows hit and I had been firing for at least a minute just taking it easy.   Then I noticed a SWARM of 20-30 arrows swaying back and forth against the wall. 
<br />

<br />
What had happened in terms of pathing was The mob was on the exact opposite side of the mountain.  For some reason as I made that corner I could just barily see the mob.  So I hailed arrows down upon the evil siren.  My arrows kept getting "netted" by the montain though.  I figured I was just missing Lol.  So I ran back figuring the mob would follow around the montain to me.  Rather than do that the mob worked its way back to the other side casting through the wall.  
<br />

<br />
It was at that point I looked up and saw my arrow swarm of death hovering.   If I moved right the arrows moved right.  Left... same thing.  Finally I ran around the wall and the siren came running at me.  I turning to find the arrows following along the wall, then around the corner and SPLAT.  Dead siren, took all the arrows at once.  multiple crits and a whole lotta hits.<br />_________________<br /><img src="http://www.eqfaces.com/photos2/azdii2.jpg" border="0" />
<br />
